250
00:24:26,181 --> 00:24:28,539
But it's alien.

251
00:24:28,540 --> 00:24:31,579
Look into its eyes.

252
00:24:42,539 --> 00:24:44,539
There you go.

253
00:24:48,059 --> 00:24:49,620
Take your time.

254
00:24:54,459 --> 00:24:56,659
It was born on a different world

255
00:24:56,660 --> 00:24:58,540
