00:46:16,300 --> 00:46:19,139
What have you done?

467
00:46:20,219 --> 00:46:23,059
Please don't. I can't let you go.

468
00:46:23,060 --> 00:46:25,780
Please. I've got to.

469
00:46:25,781 --> 00:46:27,220
I'm sorry.

470
00:46:27,221 --> 00:46:29,860
Don't, don't, don't.

471
00:46:29,861 --> 00:46:31,979
I've got to, I've got to,
I've got to.

472
00:46:36,859 --> 00:46:38,819
Put down the gun.

473
00:46:45,860 --> 00:46:49,540
Susie, it's over. Now, come with me.

474
00:47:07,060 --> 00:47:10,940
I remember. I remember.

475
00:47:14,860 --> 00:47:17,140
I remember.

476
00:48:14,180 --> 00:48:19,700
Owen and Toshiko, you didn't tell them that
you were shot in the head and survived.

477
00:48:19,701 --> 00:48:23,579
You didn't tell them either.
Followed my lead.

478
00:48:24,499 --> 00:48:28,980
Keep doing that, and you
might just get through this.

479
00:48:28,981 --> 00:48:31,619
But she killed you.

480
00:48:34,099 --> 00:48:36,580
I can't die.

481
00:48:36,581 --> 00:48:39,179
OK. But I can't.

482
00:48:41,060 --> 00:48:45,539
Something happened to me a while
back. Long story. And far away.

483
00:48:47,099 --> 00:48:48,660
But I was killed,

484
00:48:48,661 --> 00:48:52,580
and then I was brought back
to life, and ever since then...

485
00:48:52,581 --> 00:48:55,300
I can't die.

486
00:48:55,301 --> 00:48:58,260
But how? I don't know.

487
00:48:58,261 --> 00:48:59,884
One day, I'll find a doctor,

488
00:48:59,885 --> 00:49:04,059
the right sort of doctor and maybe
he can explain it. But until then...

489
00:49:04,060 --> 00:49:05,659
Nothing kills you?

490
00:49:05,660 --> 00:49:08,980
Kind of freaks people out, so...

491
00:49:08,981 --> 00:49:12,059
Best if you don't say anything.

492
00:49:12,060 --> 00:49:13,620
It doesn't matter anyway.

493
00:49:13,621 --> 00:49:16,980
You'll only wipe my memory again.
Why would I do that?

494
00:49:18,619 --> 00:49:21,380
Torchwood's got a vacancy.

495
00:49:21,381 --> 00:49:24,299
Job going spare. Do you want it?

496
00:49:24,300 --> 00:49:27,460
But what d'you need me for?

497
00:49:27,461 --> 00:49:30,380
Cos maybe you were right.

498
00:49:30,381 --> 00:49:32,740
We could do more to help.

499
00:49:35,180 --> 00:49:40,539
What d'you think,
d'you want to join up? Yeah.

500
00:49:43,259 --> 00:49:44,820
I do. Yes.

